WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.520 --> 00:00:05.066
Well, good evening, everybody.

00:00:05.066 --> 00:00:08.411
Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:00:08.926 --> 00:00:10.208
Sorry I'm late.

00:00:10.208 --> 00:00:12.896
I had a lot to do today.

00:00:13.280 --> 00:00:23.920
I'm going to go over a little bit of some of the things the Lord showed us yesterday in prayer, and we'll see if Braden had time to look at any news to see if there's any news or whatever.

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:25.600
But we're just going to pray tonight.

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:27.889
We're going to pray for our troops.

00:00:27.889 --> 00:00:34.709
As Iran says if they have a ground invasion, "We're going to burn them alive," and the things that they're saying.

00:00:34.709 --> 00:00:36.057
I say, "No, you're not.

00:00:36.331 --> 00:00:38.389
We're not going to allow that.

00:00:38.389 --> 00:00:41.989
We're going to protect them in the spirit.

00:00:41.989 --> 00:00:43.760
We're going to protect them in the natural.

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:49.048
" You know, and I truly believe that as we come together tonight, we can change things.

00:00:50.026 --> 00:00:55.424
As I was praying today, I spent most of the day in prayer.

00:00:55.424 --> 00:01:01.350
I was looking clear into July a lot, and I kept going into July, and I kept praying around July.

00:01:01.350 --> 00:01:08.120
And regardless, I'm going to be real with you for what I keep seeing: this is not going to end fast.

00:01:10.350 --> 00:01:23.920
This is something that they'll try to draw out clear into the summer, late summer, to try to keep escalating for midterms.

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:26.250
There's something more sinister behind it.

00:01:26.250 --> 00:01:49.739
But when I'm seeing it concerning midterms, praying over our troops on the ground, praying over strikes on our own bases, and continuing to pray over these lone wolf attacks and for our own electric grid, all the things concerning America, there's a lot here.

00:01:49.739 --> 00:01:52.969
And as I was praying into it, it's a lot.

00:01:52.969 --> 00:02:18.290
I told you I was talking to Diana as we were praying today, and I was really pushing hard because I know after I had that visitation from Sister Lucy that went home to be with the Lord in heaven, and Brother Hagin, the things they told me, I was practicing it today and really jumping in the rivers.

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:28.586
And I want to say this right off the bat: there's a lot of people who said, "Brandon, you're talking to the dead.

00:02:28.586 --> 00:02:32.480
You're talking to familiar spirits.

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:34.160
" No, no.

00:02:34.670 --> 00:02:40.789
I went through a portal to heaven, where I believe that I'll be one day.

00:02:40.789 --> 00:02:59.040
And if the Lord tarries, if somebody was to need to speak to me and have a word over there, and it was direction from things that were in when they were on the earth or whatever, the messages from the Lord, this isn't demonic.

00:02:59.565 --> 00:03:02.239
Some people are like, "Brandon, you're talking to familiar spirits.

00:03:02.239 --> 00:03:03.610
You're talking to the dead.

00:03:04.159 --> 00:03:06.293
" And I said, "No, this is ignorance.

00:03:06.293 --> 00:03:09.226
" Brandon would be the last person, I'm going to tell you.

00:03:09.226 --> 00:03:10.080
I know the difference.

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:27.303
And when the glory of the Lord's there, and you're in a portal, and you're talking to people that are in heaven, and you're hearing the holy angel choirs, and you're experiencing the beautiful fragrance of heaven, there's nothing demonic about it.

00:03:27.303 --> 00:03:39.280
Now, you talking to Cousin George in your house, and you're walking around talking and hearing voices in your home and knocking, you know, that's just Casper that's over there, and he's knocking on the door over there.

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:41.252
You know, "Oh, that was Grandpa.

00:03:41.252 --> 00:03:43.066
He's just visiting.

00:03:43.066 --> 00:03:46.319
" That's a demonic spirit.

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:50.400
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:54.040
The moment you die, either you're in heaven or you're going to hell.

00:03:54.040 --> 00:03:55.560
There is no in-between.

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:56.480
There's no purgatory.

00:03:56.480 --> 00:03:57.268
There's nothing.

00:03:57.531 --> 00:04:03.724
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord, or you're in hell.

00:04:03.724 --> 00:04:18.898
But I want to tell you, when you are able to go in the spirit into heaven, and see into heaven, and see the things that the Lord has for us, like even the disciples did.

00:04:18.898 --> 00:04:37.566
You know, the Book of Revelation talks all about what he was shown in a vision, and the things that he had, I believe, an out-of-body experience, with the Father showing him everything about heaven.

00:04:37.566 --> 00:04:45.680
There were a lot of things in tribulation, and we're talking over 2,000 years ago.

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:47.886
He didn't know what he was seeing.

00:04:47.886 --> 00:04:56.799
But when you're looking over, and the Lord's allowing you to look over, it's so real and it's right in front of your face.

00:04:56.799 --> 00:05:02.360
And so, a lot of people don't know what travail is.

00:05:02.360 --> 00:05:10.000
I didn't realize when the Lord said to me, "I want you to go on YouTube and teach people prayer.

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:16.640
" And I knew there were a lot of veterans that were joining up with the WWPs, with Billy's group.

00:05:33.147 --> 00:05:33.431
There are a lot of WWPs, Worldwide Prayers, that come over here.

00:05:38.340 --> 00:05:38.693
But I have a lot of babies, a lot of people.

00:05:42.520 --> 00:05:50.907
And if you remember when I told you I didn't want to do this, I was walking out, and there was a huge auditorium that was a school.

00:05:50.907 --> 00:06:06.720
It was a school, but it was a PE room, like where you go and do physical education in your school, where it would be a cafeteria or whatever, but it's cleared out for physical education classes at school, PE class.

00:06:07.070 --> 00:06:16.784
I was at a school, and there were little children everywhere at the school, and the Lord said, "Teach my people to pray.

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:21.056
" And I said, "No, I don't want to.

00:06:29.760 --> 00:06:30.000
" I walked out in this dream, and I walked out of this vast auditorium because I was hurt.

00:06:32.186 --> 00:06:34.330
I was offended by the church, and I was turned around by a whirlwind.

00:06:34.919 --> 00:06:39.291
And I could see in the sky the moon was divided in half with an eclipse.

00:06:39.291 --> 00:06:41.650
Actually, it was the sun.

00:06:42.060 --> 00:06:43.589
It was an eclipse.

00:06:43.589 --> 00:06:46.880
It wasn't the moon; it was the sun that was an eclipse.

00:06:48.880 --> 00:06:50.629
I could see it was almost completely blacked out.

00:06:57.440 --> 00:07:03.725
I could hear the sirens blowing all around me.

00:07:03.725 --> 00:07:07.566
And I could see the sky was divided with black and blue.

00:07:07.566 --> 00:07:20.916
It was completely blacked out, and one side of the sky was completely blue, and I could hear tornado sirens, and I knew there was something very wrong.

00:07:35.543 --> 00:07:36.034
And he said, "Go in and teach the children to pray.

00:07:38.400 --> 00:07:48.302
" So I went into the cafeteria where everybody was at, and everybody started sitting around me, and there were kids all around me, and he said, "Teach them.

00:07:48.302 --> 00:07:53.279
" So I started teaching prayer in this vast auditorium full of children, and I woke up.

00:07:54.898 --> 00:07:58.463
I knew then the Lord—I said, "Lord, how do I teach people to pray?

00:07:59.928 --> 00:08:00.604
I don't even know what I'm doing.

00:08:00.604 --> 00:08:02.453
What do you want me to do?

00:08:02.453 --> 00:08:03.789
" He said, "By example.

00:08:03.789 --> 00:08:11.440
Show them how to enter into the rivers, how you've learned from people, from Pastor Terry and Gina.

00:08:11.440 --> 00:08:16.023
" And there were so many that I learned from, Iva.

00:08:16.354 --> 00:08:19.520
They all led prayer, and I would listen working for the ministry.

00:08:26.360 --> 00:08:26.640
I was in the back, and I would listen to Pastor Terry.

00:08:26.640 --> 00:08:28.539
They would have prayer on Thursdays.

00:08:28.539 --> 00:08:37.501
Mondays was healing school, and I listened to that, and there were pastors leading healing school and praying for the sick and stuff on Mondays.

00:08:46.787 --> 00:08:47.200
On Thursdays, they had prayer school.

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:49.920
So I would clean and mop the foyer, and vacuum, and do prayer.

00:08:49.920 --> 00:08:55.589
They did prayer on Thursdays, and I would hear a lady named Annie; she was there and she would do prayer.

00:08:55.589 --> 00:08:58.416
There were several others.

00:08:58.416 --> 00:09:04.032
But every Thursday, I would take my breaks around.

00:09:16.250 --> 00:09:16.560
Me and a lady named Jan, she would clean with me, and we would clean the church together, and I was the church mouse.

00:09:18.540 --> 00:09:19.980
I stayed in there and I cleaned the nurseries.

00:09:19.980 --> 00:09:32.857
But I would listen to Brother Hagin, and I would listen to Pastor Terry, and I would listen to these others continually on Thursdays, and that's where I learned prayer.

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:41.172
I worked there for over four years, and I listened to the prayer every Thursday, and I just kept developing and kept developing.

00:09:41.617 --> 00:09:44.239
And then whenever I quit, I thought, "Man, I'm going into full-time ministry.

00:09:48.754 --> 00:09:49.223
" And the Lord said, "No, you're going to be an armor bearer for the pastor in Oklahoma City.

00:09:49.223 --> 00:10:00.880
" So, I went to Oklahoma City, and the Lord had me there for 13 years praying, and I did Saturday morning prayer, and I just kept working at it and working at it.

00:10:00.880 --> 00:10:06.909
There'd be, you know, 100 people show up, if that; sometimes less than 20 because it was early in the mornings on Saturdays.

00:10:06.909 --> 00:10:18.456
Long story short, I thought that was the dream until the Lord said, "I want you to go on YouTube and tell them the things that I have showed you.

00:10:18.456 --> 00:10:21.679
" But then he said, "I don't want you to do that anymore.

00:10:24.129 --> 00:10:25.299
I want you to do prayer every single time.

00:10:25.299 --> 00:10:30.089
" And I thought, "There is nobody going to come and pray on YouTube.

00:10:37.493 --> 00:10:37.760
" I mean, in my mind, that's what I'm thinking.

00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:41.748
I'm not vocalizing that; I'm saying it in my mind.

00:10:44.689 --> 00:10:47.130
And I know he hears your thoughts, but I was thinking, "Nobody's going to show up and pray.

00:10:47.130 --> 00:10:49.502
Why would anybody come and pray on YouTube?

00:10:49.502 --> 00:10:56.674
" But he said, "I want you to go live, and I want you to start doing these live prayer sessions.

00:10:58.279 --> 00:11:00.300
" I was so nervous when I first did my first one.

00:11:02.720 --> 00:11:04.119
I created a "Pray With Me" by Kenneth E.

00:11:04.119 --> 00:11:09.120
Hagin, and it went viral, and then everybody and their brother copied it and put it all over.

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:17.911
All the original "Pray With Me" that you see on there, "Pray with Kenneth Hagin for 30 minutes," came from my idea that I got from the Holy Spirit.

00:11:29.120 --> 00:11:29.320
I created that, and then the ministry took it down because I had over a million hits and they didn't want that.

00:11:37.540 --> 00:11:37.890
So they took that video down, but then it was spread so much, it was all around the world.

00:11:42.373 --> 00:11:45.480
So every one of those is an original from me creating it back then because I didn't know how to pray by myself on the internet.

00:11:45.480 --> 00:11:50.506
And so I started taking Sister Lynn and some of these other ministries, and I started making "Pray With Me.

00:11:50.506 --> 00:11:54.071
" Then the Lord said, "You're done with those.

00:11:54.071 --> 00:11:56.809
You're to pray by yourself now.

00:11:56.809 --> 00:11:59.650
" And I thought, "Pray by myself now?

00:11:59.650 --> 00:12:03.040
How am I going to do that?

00:12:03.040 --> 00:12:04.390
" He said, "Just do it.

00:12:04.390 --> 00:12:09.850
" So, I did that for about, what was it, six months, praying by myself?

00:12:09.850 --> 00:12:13.050
I'd been praying with the others for about six months, Braden.

00:12:13.050 --> 00:12:13.630
Yeah.

00:12:32.160 --> 00:12:32.462
And so, we did that.

00:12:33.671 --> 00:12:35.030
I did that, and you'll see the videos.

00:12:35.030 --> 00:12:36.079
Some of them are still there.

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:47.146
But then the Lord said, "I want you to go on live by yourself.

00:12:49.977 --> 00:12:50.210
" So, I thought, "I can't do this.

00:12:50.210 --> 00:12:51.839
I'm taking the training wheels off.

00:13:07.760 --> 00:13:08.080
" And so, that's where we are now.

00:13:08.080 --> 00:13:13.480
A lot of people wanted to know more about why I do what I do.

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:21.140
I'm just kind of answering some questions right now, but they didn't understand what groaning in the spirit was.

00:13:30.133 --> 00:13:30.360
People didn't have a clue.

00:13:38.800 --> 00:13:54.687
So I'm going to bring out clips of groaning in the spirit, what it truly is.

00:13:54.687 --> 00:13:57.500
People are saying, "Is it a demon?

00:14:12.639 --> 00:14:13.598
" I said, "No.

00:14:13.598 --> 00:14:29.280
" This is where it goes in the river, what I call these rivers, the pulses of the Holy Spirit.

00:14:49.931 --> 00:14:50.503
When you go to another level of groaning in the spirit, it's anointed prayer, but it goes into where your tongues—it's like a travail.

00:15:06.800 --> 00:15:07.120
It comes into a travail where you feel like you are birthing a child.

00:15:07.120 --> 00:15:10.639
That's what I would call it in the spirit.

00:15:10.639 --> 00:15:21.645
Now, I know a woman's going to say, "Brandon, you have no idea what you're talking about.

00:15:21.645 --> 00:15:25.623
" I'm doing the best I can, ladies.

00:15:25.623 --> 00:15:27.173
I'm sorry.

00:15:27.173 --> 00:15:39.457
My wife, of course, could tell you, like any other woman who has had children, what it's like to go through labor, but a man has no idea.

00:15:39.457 --> 00:15:47.520
So I try to do my best of explaining what I feel like it is in the spirit: it's birthing something in the spirit.

00:15:55.839 --> 00:15:56.399
It's birthing.

00:15:56.399 --> 00:15:58.426
So it's groanings.

00:15:58.426 --> 00:16:03.314
It comes up out of your spirit, but it's deeper than just tongues.

00:16:03.314 --> 00:16:04.489
It's deeper than tongues.

00:16:04.489 --> 00:16:22.320
And so I know Romans, when Lucy was talking about it to me in heaven, she said, "Likewise, the Spirit also helpeth our infirmities, for we know not what we should pray for as we ought, but the Spirit itself maketh intercession for us with groanings which cannot be uttered.

00:16:22.320 --> 00:16:26.711
" Now, I know that's the King James Version.

00:16:26.711 --> 00:16:31.190
Other people are saying, "Brandon, it says it better in other versions.

00:16:31.190 --> 00:16:38.098
" We just usually stick with the King James, but we don't know what to pray, so he's praying through us, because of John.

00:16:38.098 --> 00:16:40.800
Can you give that one?

00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:42.811
John, I believe, is what it is.

00:16:46.480 --> 00:16:46.720
You could have put it right there in that search, honey.

00:16:46.720 --> 00:16:49.817
No, I gave you the wrong verse.

00:16:49.817 --> 00:16:52.679
Diana, ask her what that verse was.

00:16:52.679 --> 00:16:54.480
She knows it by heart.

00:16:54.480 --> 00:16:56.320
She memorized it a while ago.

00:16:56.320 --> 00:16:57.940
Diana has a photographic memory.

00:16:57.940 --> 00:17:00.919
She's very, very intelligent, and she memorizes a lot of verses.

00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:04.880
I'm sorry, but she'll bring it.

00:17:04.880 --> 00:17:09.679
But what I'm trying to tell you all is that the Holy Spirit dwells in us.

00:17:19.160 --> 00:17:19.329
And when you yield to him, scripture, John.

00:17:19.329 --> 00:17:19.669
Yeah.

00:17:19.669 --> 00:17:19.999
John.

00:17:22.026 --> 00:17:22.480
I said John.

00:17:33.360 --> 00:17:33.520
See the International Version.

00:17:33.520 --> 00:17:35.097
John is what it was.

00:17:35.097 --> 00:17:36.844
Oh, you're on verse four.

00:17:36.844 --> 00:17:37.840
You got to go down, hon.

00:17:37.840 --> 00:17:41.120
14, all the way down.

00:17:41.120 --> 00:17:43.006
8, 9, 10, 15...

00:17:43.006 --> 00:17:46.422
15, right there.

00:17:46.925 --> 00:17:47.679
"The Spirit of truth.

00:17:50.845 --> 00:17:55.920
The world cannot accept him, because it neither sees him nor knows him.

00:18:09.919 --> 00:18:10.399
But you know him, for he lives with you and will be in you.

00:18:10.399 --> 00:18:16.053
" So we know him because he's in us.

00:18:19.813 --> 00:18:43.200
But as we dwell with him and he dwells with us, when we yield ourselves over to the Spirit of God, when we yield ourselves over to the Holy Spirit to pray through us, when we know not what we ought to pray, the groanings come forth through that.

00:18:51.780 --> 00:18:52.160
And it's not weird.

00:18:56.107 --> 00:18:56.400
It is a deeper level of tongues.

00:19:15.420 --> 00:19:15.590
And that's what Lucy was trying to say to me in heaven.

00:19:15.590 --> 00:19:19.440
She said, "You're not going to get there just by praying in the spirit.

00:19:21.713 --> 00:19:21.919
You're going to have to groan.

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:27.177
This is going to have to come through travail.

00:19:30.640 --> 00:19:30.920
" It comes through a deeper level of tongues.

00:19:30.920 --> 00:19:39.280
For the greater glory will be attached to travail, and it will be as the Holy Spirit is guiding you in prayer.

00:19:39.280 --> 00:19:41.650
It's not where you just flow.

00:19:45.880 --> 00:19:51.870
And the more you get into heavy intercession, it will feel like you're in a travail over it, and you'll be praying it out, and you'll know.

00:20:00.914 --> 00:20:01.509
You can't make it up, and the flesh doesn't get involved in it.

00:20:01.509 --> 00:20:06.799
You'll know when it's truly the Holy Spirit, and you'll feel it.

00:20:06.799 --> 00:20:09.120
But usually, it's when you hit those rivers.

00:20:18.834 --> 00:20:19.063
It's when you get over in the spirit instead of just praying in the flesh.

00:20:19.291 --> 00:20:25.253
You can pray in tongues, but there's a big difference when I'm telling you I can feel it when I hit that river.

00:20:33.280 --> 00:20:33.552
It's like I say, I'm trying to find a vein.

00:20:33.552 --> 00:20:35.456
You're trying to find a vein.

00:20:35.456 --> 00:20:36.756
I try to find it.

00:20:36.756 --> 00:20:38.080
That's why I'm looking for it.

00:20:40.672 --> 00:20:42.016
I'm looking for His guidance because He's in me.

00:20:42.016 --> 00:20:43.349
Just like it says right there.

00:20:43.349 --> 00:20:51.520
I'm sorry, I haven't read it over and over again, so I don't have it down.

00:20:51.520 --> 00:20:53.413
So, if my reading is bad, I apologize.

00:21:08.280 --> 00:21:08.800
"The Spirit of truth.

00:21:15.520 --> 00:21:15.740
The world cannot accept Him because it neither sees Him nor knows Him.

00:21:15.740 --> 00:21:18.240
" They don't see Him, and they don't know Him.

00:21:18.240 --> 00:21:20.360
But He is dwelling in you.

00:21:20.360 --> 00:21:22.520
That's what I try to tell y'all.

00:21:22.520 --> 00:21:24.663
You are wall-to-wall Holy Spirit.

00:21:30.560 --> 00:21:30.960
He dwells the moment you accept Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal savior.

00:21:36.731 --> 00:21:37.006
He's there standing at the door saying, "I want to be your friend.

00:21:40.823 --> 00:21:49.578
" And the moment you start being friends with the Holy Spirit and open that door for Him, He comes in and says, "Hey, let's have fellowship.

00:21:49.578 --> 00:21:50.846
Let's talk.

00:21:50.846 --> 00:21:54.114
Let's have a glass of tea.

00:21:54.114 --> 00:21:55.623
" This is tea.

00:21:55.623 --> 00:22:00.065
This is unsweet tea, too.

00:22:00.065 --> 00:22:07.354
My little girl asked for canes tonight.

00:22:07.354 --> 00:22:20.777
And I told her, I said, "Okay, Daddy will get you some tea.

00:22:37.200 --> 00:22:37.450
" But He dwells in you, and He's your friend.

00:22:37.450 --> 00:22:38.450
He's your standby.

00:22:38.450 --> 00:22:43.540
He's an ever-present help in a time of need.

00:22:53.708 --> 00:22:53.919
"But the Spirit of truth, the world cannot accept Him because it neither sees Him nor knows Him.

00:22:53.919 --> 00:22:59.680
But you know Him, for He lives with you and will be in you.

00:22:59.680 --> 00:23:05.920
" We know Him because He's in us and He's with us.

00:23:05.920 --> 00:23:10.262
So we're just yielding to the Holy Spirit, and the groanings come out of that.

00:23:19.760 --> 00:23:20.023
I hope I don't butcher that.

00:23:23.919 --> 00:23:24.174
I try my best.

00:23:24.174 --> 00:23:29.164
I'm working on being a better teacher of prayer and stuff, but I try not to make it too complicated.

00:23:30.211 --> 00:23:30.735
I love this right here.

00:23:30.735 --> 00:23:32.240
Can you play my friend?

00:23:36.144 --> 00:23:36.392
This is my friend.

00:23:47.780 --> 00:23:48.280
You turn me off.

00:24:14.000 --> 00:24:14.640
I depend on Him to move through this flawed vessel.

00:24:14.640 --> 00:24:18.594
He still seems to do that.

00:24:18.594 --> 00:24:22.400
I'm amazed, as you are, that it happens.

00:24:22.400 --> 00:24:27.240
I'm amazed that He did it, and I'm amazed that He used me to do it.

